A vast horizontal landscape in cyberpunk style showing two massive glowing server towers standing like futuristic skyscrapers on opposite ends of a neon-lit Chinese cityscape at night. Between them, streams of luminescent data particles flow like rivers, splitting and merging in complex patterns. The servers are adorned with intricate circuit-board patterns that pulse with electric blue and magenta light. In the background, a stylized Great Wall extends across the horizon, reimagined as a network backbone with fiber optic cables running along its length. The sky is dark with hints of digital rain falling. The scene conveys scale, connectivity, and the challenge of distributing computational power across a massive infrastructure, with a distinctly Asian megacity aesthetic blending ancient architectural silhouettes with bleeding-edge technology.
